high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the butter knife from the sink table.
Turn and go near the lettuce.
Cut the lettuce into pieces using the knife.
Turn around and go near the dining table.
Put the butter knife on the dining table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the piece of lettuce from the sink table.
Turn around and go near the dining table.
Put the piece of lettuce on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the butter knife and piece of lettuce on the dining table.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right.
Pick up butter knife from the sink.
Turn back again on the same position
Slice lettuce on the sink
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the dining table.
Place butter knife on the dining table.
Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the sink on your right.
Pick sliced lettuce on hand
Turn around and turn left and then head straight towards the dining table.
Pick sliced lettuce on dining table
anns.task_desc: Slicing lettuce and placing it on dining table

high_descs: Turn right and go towards the countertop where the sink is
Pick up the butter knife on the countertop
Move to your left towards the lettuce
Cut the lettuce into slices
Turn around and go to the dining table on your left
Put the butter knife on the left side next to the bread
Go back to the sink countertop towards the lettuce
Pick up a slice of lettuce
Turn around and go back to the dining table
Put the lettuce next to the butter knife on the dining table
anns.task_desc: Put a butter knife with lettuce on a dining table
